Everyone in Riverwood called her crazy, but She would not be deterred. Grabbing her bow, she headed up the pass towards Bleak Falls Barrow. Treasure awaits, one must but be bold enough to grab it!

descriptionHtml:
Everyone in Riverwood called her crazy, but She would not be deterred. Grabbing her bow, she headed up the pass towards Bleak Falls Barrow. Treasure awaits, one must but be bold enough to grab it!

Lyara is a custom follower, she awaits you in somewhere Bleak Falls Barrow, having bit off more than she can chew.

Body: CBBE HDT SillyHuge
Hair: KS Hairdo's
Eyes: The Eyes of beauty 

All these need be installed. 

Comments & suggestions welcome.

This is my second follower mod, and I'm quite pleased with the outcome. First one's face came out a bit off from the export I did with RaceMenu. This one came out perfect. I'll re-export Prisilla at some time and redo her to fix the face issue now that I know it was my error, and not some CK weirdness. :P
